Text: Thank youWeakly and I delivered stuffed Operation Christmas Child shoeboxes to the Omaha distribution point yesterday It was quite a sight to see thousands of gaily wrapped shoeboxes against the back wall Northern Border paid the shipping costs thank you Northern Border From here the boxes will go to Minneapolis and from Minneapolis they will be shipped around the world Volunteers like you and me will place them in the hands of precious children in pretty tragic circumstances giving them a bright spot they will probably never forget Thank you so much everyone for your selflessness You just HAVE to be the greatest J
